{"tid":1869423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HAEA：收集各聯網各醫院各部門的打壓證據，繼續抗爭","createTime":"2020-02-08T07:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T15:34:34.000Z","uid":221035,"like":89,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2fa664460efbf2fcdb7e5782841d3a6c97ee27","tid":1869423,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"小休過後，以為HAEA會就此罷休?<br />\n醫管局你唔好以為自己贏咗，你已經輸哂二萬名員工嘅信任！<br />\n<br />\n唔即時處理問題，唔接見前線員工，玩拖字訣，唔尊重有二萬名會員嘅工會，再對員工秋後算賬，正正就是每位年薪過幾百萬的管理層躲在辦公室裡的工作！<br />\n<br />\n我哋將會收集各聯網各醫院各部門的打壓證據，例如，已收到同事反映原定8/2 Night shift 同事被迫放AL，老屈同事曠工....於整合後我哋會一炮過向管理層要求解釋！詳情將於稍後時間公布！<br />\n<br />\n至於法律問題，知道大家都好擔心，<br />\n我哋都希望可以搞一場法律講座俾大家參與，釋除大家疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n而有關確保PPE貨存量一事，管理層開會時一直交唔出數字，跟住暫停延長罷工計劃就即刻有數字？<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379812&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=4abdacca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379812&h=1fe679d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379812</a><br />\n<br />\n//醫管局指，現時外科口罩存倉量約1600萬個，保護衣則有220萬件，未計算已分發到各部門的裝備，存倉量只夠使用一個月。醫管局已添購一批口罩，但未來的供應有變數。//<br />\n<br />\n//他表示，政府已承諾有需要時向醫管局提供口罩。他不同意定期公開防疫裝備數量，認為只會加重員工工作量，對提升裝備數量沒有用處。//<br />\n<br />\n面對住咁嘅管理層，我哋一定要集合力量，團結一致作出反抗！<br />\n我哋唔希望見到大家灰心，失望，覺得依場仗打輸咗；<br />\n事實上我哋嘅行動令到政府逐步封關，令政府開始14日強制檢疫 (但點知個內容係咁令人失望...🙄)<br />\n希望大家同我哋一樣，失意過後，振作起來，繼續爭取我哋嘅五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭之路，正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/posts/140375877433553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHA.EmployAlliance%2Fposts%2F140375877433553&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=d88bd1e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/posts/140375877433553</a>"},{"pid":"a882769925ceeb776b3bd4519bf0790a770e6bb5","tid":1869423,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1029f024d2618ae196cca6fca409440c19d36ed","tid":1869423,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135b620c12119ec133e2574f98ff22c8927f3047","tid":1869423,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56808a0e4b27765745c2884ffe3f36b9acb19508","tid":1869423,"uid":199893,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"罷工完咗唔代表HAEA嘅抗爭完咗"},{"pid":"b161134729a9e5b172857aa1ddb9ebbc86a95e24","tid":1869423,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d8947f50ce247dbcf76263ec3d47581f1f1a12b","tid":1869423,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55372da278390dbdc08fabe4696bfb9514669f36","tid":1869423,"uid":156057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be403390aed8001da514e7027f3122539980475","tid":1869423,"uid":263709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"進<br />\n東區醫院上星期話得1成PPE剩番"},{"pid":"4b55614484b2e0ffb79a4ac8ab954ab447774333","tid":1869423,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"G 持"},{"pid":"df86fdf299e65214fb67f61de07b1bc7b739578c","tid":1869423,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆